# CoinFrenzy Casino — Cursor Rules

You are working on the CoinFrenzy casino platform — a sweepstakes social
casino that will replace the operator's existing Gamma platform. This
codebase has been pre-designed in detail. Your job is to implement what's
already designed, not to redesign it.

---

## The constitution

The `/docs` folder is the source of truth. There are 13 architecture
documents totaling ~11,000 lines. Before you write code for a task, you
MUST read the relevant doc.

The mapping from task to doc:

| Task type | Read this doc first |
