## When you're done with a session

Always end with a summary of:
1. What was completed
2. What was NOT completed (if anything was left for next session)
3. What the user should verify before moving on
4. Which prompt file is next

The user is following a numbered sequence of prompts. He needs to know
where he is in that sequence at all times.
